          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "CHSEP",
                "ASPEC",
                "XSPEC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Immediately following the",
                "irradiation, the catcher foil was dissolved in hot 8M",
                "HNO, in the presence of Hg+2. The berkelium products",
                "were oxidized to +4 using CrO, and were extracted",
                "into bis (2-ethylhexyl) orthophosphoric acid (HDEHP)",
                "in n- dodecane. The berkelium products were plated on",
                "1-inch diameter platinum disks for x-ray, gamma,",
                "and/or alpha counting. The time from the end of the",
                "bombardment (eob) to the start of counting was 12-14",
                "min with a chemical yield of 50%."
              ]
            }
          ],
